{"tid":1154781,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱喺恒大屌到不Gay的瘋巴打跪喺度喊","createTime":"2019-05-14T13:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T16:02:44.000Z","uid":129042,"like":198,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4ecfe89cbb4ee26137556c850b7161df140bd468","tid":1154781,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早排聽講不Gay的瘋巴打好鐘意周圍去唔同嘅大學屌柒啲大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁今日咁啱冇走堂留咗喺學校<br />\n又咁啱比我見到不Gay真人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢樣衰頭柒，身高應該得160<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n離遠睇以為有小學生嚟參觀<br />\n仲要成頭油仲要有陣臭狐味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過門都係客呀<br />\n咪招呼下佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不Gay的瘋：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：Hi,你有冇見到恒大嘅大學生？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：在下正是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩幫到你？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩，唔撚係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你...DSE幾多分呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我六科加埋都有3分嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我IVE入嚟嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩屌你老母！！呀！<br />\n<br />\n不Gay的瘋聽見我得3分都入到恒大，即刻嚇到退咗幾步， 一唔小心失咗重心，仆左喺偉倫廣場塊空地嗰到<br />\n<br />\n我都唔執輸，事前已經知佢想挑我地恒大機，想屌到我地跪喺到，唔係咁易架葉師傅。<br />\n所以先發制人吹大雞<br />\n叫咗我哋恒大翼嵐天八子出嚟坐陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8yj8VbO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8yj8VbO.png&h=eb233174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八子異口同聲喝鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢成日叫啲00後跪低認錯<br />\n應該估唔到有一日跪喺度嘅喺佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n八子：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n八子 + me：屌你老母好心你洗下頭先入嚟我地恒大範圍啦，衛生署應該捉你條毒撚去人道毀滅呀！<br />\n<br />\n我地一路屌，佢就一路趴喺到喊，條褲仲濕咗，可能喺比我地嚇到瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍仲有好多女同學指住佢嚟笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢咁可憐<br />\n我地先放佢一馬<br />\n仲畀咗條恒大Logo嘅紙底褲畀佢換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢先爬住咁走咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：恒大仔好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：Pound of my school<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab82